attributedString.string:
1.	Getting Started: (this one), instruction on how to use the kit.
	2.	Whats New: An overview of whats been added to the kit since the last version. 
	3.	Style: The core visual styles of Carbon, including typography, color and more.
	4.	Grid: Default artboards and the Carbon grid system for responsive web design.
	5.	Components: A collection of all assets that correspond to the Carbon Design System and Component Library.
	6.	Layout templates: Examples of different ways Carbon components and styles can be used in layouts.
	7.	Data Viz: A collection of data viz elements, styles, and examples.
